---
title: Conney the Corgi!
pageable: true
---

- page_articles.each do |article|
  %article
    %h1
      %a{ href: article.url }= article.title
      %time= article.date.strftime('%Y/%m/%d')
    = article.body
    %a{ href: article.url } Read more
- if paginate
  .paginate
    - if prev_page
      %span.prev
        %a{ href: prev_page.url } Prev
    - if next_page
      %span.next
        %a{ href: next_page.url } Next
